{"type":null,"faqId":44320,"title":"如何设置短信骚扰拦截？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-family:微软雅黑;color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n</p>\n\"1. 您好，手机管家的电话拦截功能只能拦截黑名单、陌生人和未知号码，需要在手机管家进行设置( “骚扰拦截 &gt; 设置 &gt; 拦截规则“)。拦截规则有四个选项，分别是智能拦截，拦截黑名单，拦截陌生人，拦截未知号码。智能拦截只能拦截短信，拦截黑名单需要用户把不想接听号码添加到黑名单里（“设置 &gt; 黑名单 &gt; 添加”），拦截陌生人是拦截通讯录以外的电话和短信，拦截未知号码是拦截空号码、私人号码、不可知号码。目前版本的手机管家没用号码段拦截功能，如需该功能，请使用第三方APP。<br>\n2. 进入“信息 &gt; 骚扰拦截”，选择要加入黑名单的联系人，点击“确定”。\"\n<br>\n<br>\n<p>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":2,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9820","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400459000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":51,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"设置,短信,拦截,骚扰","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}